# ELK Garden — environment is split by app:
#
# 1) Backend (Express): copy backend/.env.example → backend/.env
#    - OPENAI_API_KEY
#    - ELK_API_PORT (optional)
#
# 2) Frontend (Vite): copy frontend/.env.example → frontend/.env.local
#    - VITE_API_BASE (e.g. http://localhost:8788)
#
# Do not put secrets in the repo root .env file.
